### Remaining Concerns

None structural. Two adequate-but-not-explicit transitions were left alone on purpose: runwayв†’reading-list (the "first-aid kit" opener already carries the safety theme) and black-boxв†’stops-preparing (the H2 itself asks the question the first sentence answers). Bridging those would risk the mechanical-transition pattern the piece currently avoids. Lint confirms: 0 fail, 1 pre-existing warn.
